{"tid":850322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【屯門新盤】580萬買上源兩房 黃先生：落女友個名！","createTime":"2018-10-06T11:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T06:01:41.000Z","uid":64694,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0d560d1503208a64eafb5f3fb9d9366af6468bc9","tid":850322,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:30:57.000Z","msg":"內房萬科香港屯門新盤上源今日次輪推售310伙，發展商稱日前累收約3,500票，超額認購超過10倍。<br />\n<br />\n廿四孝男友、90後從事金融科技的黃先生表示，今次買樓同女友計劃了1年多買樓，就算加息都不影響置業計劃。他說：「就落女友名，自己就幫手供樓。」<br />\n<br />\n他表示，因為自己居住及工作都是在新界區，所以不擔心交通問題，是次斥買入3A座中層B室，實用468方呎2房，約580萬2房，首期支付120萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181006/large/1538817005_f445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181006%2Flarge%2F1538817005_f445.jpg&h=81478975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181006/58763106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58763106&d=o4wvVtgZmRjIJ0dfGq4TaozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=c8ceddcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58763106&h=6be40c6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181006/58763106</a>"},{"pid":"b4343f0c1fcfd09831e13cda579901d0e7f12439","tid":850322,"uid":135767,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:07:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d924539a8d07190f2c64dfdcce6e0e93b6dc2301","tid":850322,"uid":182499,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:14:39.000Z","msg":"係咪地產仔扮買家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd659e4c38a8f8d62c15ff8ec25c53b2643ae1b","tid":850322,"uid":197640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-